  "detailed_description": "Harmonia is a digital novel made by visual novel studio Key.<br>There are no story branches based on choices. The story proceeds as if you were watching an anime or movie, or turning the pages of a novel.<br>Enjoy a touching story with beautiful music and graphics, realistic and colorful performances, brought to life by talented voice actors.<br><br><strong>Game features</strong><br>・With support for full HD resolution of 1920x1080 dots, you can enjoy the moving story in high-definition visuals.<br><br>・The text can be set to English, Japanese, or Simplified Chinese (audio only available in Japanese). This includes in-game text, options, and the digital manual. Language settings can be changed at any time.<br><br>・Protagonist Rei, as well as twenty-six background characters, are all given voices for the first time.<br><br>・Touch gestures can also be used if you're playing on a tablet PC or a Steam Deck.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/d348af7ea8eb44725d834c152a6513bd.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=658 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/719c17c6af2a10e46ed5adb1664303ed.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/537c45d329bf216b2f0a3ea27ccab912.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=369 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/e98a103fa7b3c311bcb432c10813a2fb.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=369 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/bdd14cfd3e71cf71788ab7ae4be6076f.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=369 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/2bbe8a00e34470329ec2ad8389996f6e.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=369 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/8bc2e05b6476afa5000cfb35f4ecd864.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=484 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Harmonia is a digital novel made by visual novel studio Key.<br>There are no story branches based on choices. The story proceeds as if you were watching an anime or movie, or turning the pages of a novel.<br>Enjoy a touching story with beautiful music and graphics, realistic and colorful performances, brought to life by talented voice actors.<br><br><strong>Game features</strong><br>・With support for full HD resolution of 1920x1080 dots, you can enjoy the moving story in high-definition visuals.<br><br>・The text can be set to English, Japanese, or Simplified Chinese (audio only available in Japanese). This includes in-game text, options, and the digital manual. Language settings can be changed at any time.<br><br>・Protagonist Rei, as well as twenty-six background characters, are all given voices for the first time.<br><br>・Touch gestures can also be used if you're playing on a tablet PC or a Steam Deck.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/d348af7ea8eb44725d834c152a6513bd.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=658 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/719c17c6af2a10e46ed5adb1664303ed.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/537c45d329bf216b2f0a3ea27ccab912.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=369 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/e98a103fa7b3c311bcb432c10813a2fb.avif?t=1732683414\" width=616 height=369 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2699690/extras/bdd14cfd3e71cf7